veloped symptoms after visiting [[Passo del Tonale]] in [[Trentino]] region in Italy. The woman has been tested for coronavirus at an undisclosed private clinic. The positive result was unofficial, but in the afternoon it was confirmed by the Czech National Reference Laboratory. The woman is in quarantine at [[Bulovka Hospital]] and her family is self-quarantined at home.<ref name=case6b>{{cite web|url=https://www.novinky.cz/zahranicni/koronavirus/clanek/primator-hrib-predbehl-hygieniky-ministra-i-premiera-a-ohlasil-novy-nepotvrzeny-pripad-koronaviru-40315472|title=Prim\u00e1tor H\u0159ib p\u0159edb\u011bhl hygieniky, ministra i premi\u00e9ra a ohl\u00e1sil nov\u00fd, ov\u0161em nepotvrzen\u00fd, p\u0159\u00edpad koronaviru |website=novinky.cz |language=cs |access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref> The patient has moved from [[Bulovka Hospital]] to home quarantine on 9 March 2020.<ref name=\"mar09.BulovkaRelease\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''7'''<ref name=\"case7-8\">{{cite web|url=https://www.idnes.cz/zpravy/domaci/koronavirus-bilance-osm-lidi-v-cesku-pacienti.A200304_155319_domaci_remy|title=Testy prok\u00e1zaly dal\u0161\u00ed t\u0159\u00ed p\u0159\u00edpady koronaviru v \u010cesku, celkem je jich osm|website=Mlad\u00e1 fronta DNES|language=cs |date=4 March 2020|access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 4 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Auronzo di Cadore]]\n| [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]]\n| [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem Region]]\n| {{Partial failure|Masaryk Hospital, [[\u00dast\u00ed nad Labem]]}}\n| Male\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{flag|CZE}}\n|- class=\"expand-child\"\n| colspan=\"10\" | A husband of the infected woman from [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]] (case #4).\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=2 style=\"text-align:center;\" | '''8'''<ref name=\"case7-8\"/>\n| 4 March 2020\n| {{Partial failure|Confirmed}}\n| {{Success|Travel-related}}\n| {{flag|Italy}}, [[Auronzo di Cadore]]\n| [[D\u011b\u010d\u00edn]