e       = Tring\n|score      = 21 \u2013 26 \n|report     = [http://www.tringrugby.com/news/belated-report-on-the-1st-xvs-final-battle-against-1628182.html Tring Rangers]<br>[http://www.pitchero.com/clubs/guildford/news/guildford-promoted-to-national-3-1608145.html Guildford]\n|away       = Guildford\n|stadium    = Pendley Sports Centre\n|attendance = 700\n|referee    = \n}}\n----\n\n==2014\u201315==\n\n===Participating teams and locations===\n*[[Basingstoke R.F.C.|Basingstoke]] '''(relegated from [[National League 3 London & SE]])'''\n*[[Brighton Football Club (RFU)|Brighton]]\n*[[Charlton Park Rugby Football Club|Charlton Park]] '''(promoted from [[London 2 South East]])'''\n*[[Chobham Rugby Football Club|Chobham]] \n*[[Cobham RFC|Cobham]]\n*Dover\n*[[Gosport and Fareham R.F.C.|Gosport & Fareham]] '''(promoted from [[London 2 South West]])'''\n*[[Guildford Rugby Football Club|Guildford]]\n*[[Havant RFC|Havant]]\n*[[Hove RFC|Hove]]\n*Sidcup\n*[[Sutton & Epsom RFC|Sutton & Epsom]]\n*Twickenham '''(level transferred from [[London 1 North]])'''\n*[[Wimbledon RFC|Wimbledon]]\n\n==2013\u201314==\n\n===Participating teams and locations===\n*[[Beckenham Rugby Football Club|Beckenham]]\n*[[Brighton Football Club (RFU)|Brighton]] '''(promoted from [[London 2 South East]])'''\n*Chichester\n*[[Chobham Rugby Football Club|Chobham]] '''(promoted from [[London 2 South West]])'''\n*[[Cobham RFC|Cobham]]\n*Dover\n*[[Gravesend RFC|Gravesend]]\n*[[Havant RFC|Havant]]\n*[[Haywards Heath RFC|Haywards Heath]]\n*[[Hove RFC|Hove]]\n*Sidcup\n*[[Staines Rugby Football Club|Staines]] '''(relegated from [[National League 3 London & SE]])'''\n*[[Sutton & Epsom RFC]] '''(promoted from [[London 2 South West]])'''\n*[[Wimbledon RFC]]\n\n==2012\u201313==\n\n===Participating teams and locations===\n*[[Basingstoke R.F.C.|Basingstoke]]\n*[[Beckenham Rugby Football Club|Beckenham]]\n*[[Chichester RFC|Chichester]]\n*[[Cobham RFC|Cobham]]\n*Dover\n*[[East Grinstead RFC|East Grinstead]]\n*[[Gosport and Fareham R.F.C.|Gosport & Fareham]]\n*[[Havant RFC|Havant]] '''(relegated from [[National League 3 London & SE]])'''\n*[[Haywards Heath RFC|Haywards Heath]]\n*[[Hove RFC|Hove]]\n*[[Old Colfeians]] '''(transferred from [[London 1 North]]''')\n*[[Trojans Rugby Club|Trojans]]\n*Sidcup\n*[[Sutton & Epsom RFC]]\n*[[Wimbledon RFC|Wimbledon]]\n\n==2011\u201312==\n\n===Participating teams and locations===\n*[[Basingstoke R.F.C.|Basingstoke]]\n*[[Beckenham Rugby Football Club|Beckenham]]\n*[[Chichester RFC|Chichester]]\n*[[Cobham RFC|Cobham]]\n*Dover\n*[[Guernsey RFC|Guernsey]]\n*[[Haywards Heath RFC|Haywards Heath]]\n*[[Hove RFC|Hove]] \n*[[Old Elthamians]]\n*[[Portsmouth RFC]]\n*Sidcup\n*[[Sutton & Epsom RFC]]\n*Thanet Wanderers\n*[[Trojans Rugby Club|Trojans RFC]]\n\n==London 1 South honours==\nIn the first season of the English rugby union league pyramid, sponsored by Courage, there was six, tier six leagues. The initial name was London 2 South and was for teams based in London and the counties of Hampshire, Kent, Sussex and Surrey. There was eleven teams in the league and each team played one match against each of the other teams, giving each team five home matches and five away matches. The winning team was awarded two points, and there was one point for each team in a drawn match.<ref name=courage91>{{cite book|editor1-last=Williams|editor1-first=Tony|editor2-last=Mitchell|editor2-first=Bill|title=Courage Official Rugby Union Club Directory 1990\u201391|publisher=Football Directories|location=Taunton|isbn=1 873057 01 6|edition=3rd}}</ref>\n\n===London 2 South===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n|colspan=\"11\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"|<!--\n-->\n{| border=\"0\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"\n|-\n| style=\"width:20%; border:0;\"|\n| style=\"border:0;\"|'''London 2 South'''\n| style=\"width:20%; border:0;\"|\n|}\n|-\n!  style=\"background:#efefef; width:80px;\"|Season\n!  style=\"background:#efefef; width:5