ley]]}}|position=left|label_size=80}} \n{{location map~|UK England Southeast|lat=50.83761|long=-.774936|label={{background color|white|[[Chichester RFC|Chichester]]}}|position=right|label_size=80}} \n{{location map~|UK England Southeast|lat=51.3384958|long=-0.3959717|label={{background color|white|[[Cobham RFC|Cobham]]}}|position=bottom|label_size=80}} \n{{location map~|UK England Southeast|lat=50.8518324|long=-.9847132|label={{background color|white|[[Havant RFC|Havant]]}}|position=top|label_size=80}} \n{{location map~|UK England Southeast|lat=51.0559387|long=-0.2952787|label={{background color|white|[[Horsham Rugby Club|Horsham]]}}|position=right|label_size=80}} \n{{location map~|UK England Southeast|lat=51.531908 |long=0.039406 |label={{background color|white|London}}|position=left|label_size=80}} \n{{location map~|UK England Southeast|lat=51.3746569|long=0.4939288|label={{background color|white|[[Medway RFC|Medway]]}}|position=bottom|label_size=80}} \n{{location map~|UK England Southeast|lat=51.4984207|long=0.3476118|label={{background color|white|[[Thurrock Rugby Football Club|Thurrock]]}}|position=top|label_size=80}} \n\n{{Location map~ |UK England Southeast|mark=TransparentPlaceholder.png |marksize=1 |lat=50.4 |long=-0.6 |label=<div style=\"font-size:80%;\">'''[[London]]&nbsp;teams'''<br>\n[[Beckenham Rugby Football Club|Beckenham]]<br>\n[[Belsize Park RFC|Belsize Park]]<br>\n[[Dartfordians RFC|Dartfordians]]<br>\n[[Honourable Artillery Company RFC|H.A.C.]]<br>\n[[King's College School Old Boys RFC|KCS Old Boys]]<br>\n[[London Cornish RFC|L Cornish]]<br>\n[[Westcombe Park Rugby Football Club|Westcombe&nbsp;Park]]\n</div>|position=right}}\n}}\n\n{{col-break|width=10%}}\n\n{{Location map+|Greater London\n |caption=Location of 2019\u201320 London 1 South teams in London\n |alt=Location of London 1 South teams in London\n |float=right\n |width=250\n |places =\n {{Location map~|Greater London|lat=51.3965988|long=-0.0391510|label={{background color|white|'''[[Becke