g]] (1){{#tag:ref|Barking's league title was won when the league was known as London 1.|group=a}}\n*[[Barnes Rugby Football Club|Barnes]] (1)\n*[[Charlton Park Rugby Football Club|Charlton Park]] (1){{#tag:ref|Charlton Park's league title was won when the league was known as London 1.|group=a}} \n*[[CS Rugby 1863]] (1)\n*[[Dorking R.F.C.|Dorking]] (1)\n*[[East Grinstead Rugby Football Club|East Grinstead]] (1)\n*[[Guernsey RFC|Guernsey]] (1)\n*[[Old Alleynian Football Club|Old Alleynian]] (1)\n*[[Old Colfeians]] (1)\n*[[Old Mid-Whitgiftian RFC|Old Mid-Whitgiftian]] (1)\n*[[Portsmouth Rugby Football Club|Portsmouth]] (1)\n*[[Richmond F.C.|Richmond]] (1)\n*[[Sevenoaks RFC|Sevenoaks]] (1)\n*[[Sidcup RFC|Sidcup]] (1)\n*[[Thanet Wanderers RUFC|Thanet Wanderers]] (1)\n*[[Tonbridge Juddians Rugby Football Club|Tonbridge Juddians]] (1)\n*[[Westcombe Park RFC|Westcombe Park]] (1)\n*[[Wimbledon RFC|Wimbledon]] (1)\n*[[Winchester RFC|Winchester]] (1)\n*[[Worthing Rugby Football Club|Worthing]] (1)\n\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|group=a}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[London and South East Division Rugby Football Union|London & SE Division RFU]]\n* [[Hampshire Rugby Football Union|Hampshire RFU]]\n* [[Kent Rugby Football Union|Kent RFU]]\n* [[Surrey Rugby Football Union|Surrey RFU]]\n* [[Sussex Rugby Football Union|Sussex RFU]]\n* [[English rugby union system]]\n* [[Rugby union in England]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|3}}\n\n{{Rugby union in England}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:London 1 South}}\n[[Category:Rugby union leagues in England|6]]\n[[Category:Rugby union leagues in London|2]]\n[[Category:Recurring sporting events established in 1987]]\n[[Category:Sports leagues established in 1987]]\n", "name_user": "Crouch, Swale", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguating links toGrays(link changed toGrays, Essex; link changed toGrays, Essex; link changed toGrays, Essex) usingDisamAssist.", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/London_1_South"}
